KEQ7kNvgH5mpEi&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCkf4lCocgbbeQVy5I8VsWmorTR23w_2CyU_ZpQhtwv6A&oe=66CDCC7B"}, "display_name": "Strike Master", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Strike Master: The Ultimate VR Bowling Experience\n\nWelcome to \"Strike Master,\" where the classic sport of bowling transcends the ordinary and enters a realm of immersive virtual reality. Get ready to embark on a cosmic adventure that transforms traditional bowling into an exhilarating and futuristic experience. Whether you're a seasoned bowler or new to the game, \"Strike Master\" offers a fresh and captivating way to enjoy this beloved sport.\nGame Overview\n\n\"Strike Master\" is a cutting-edge VR game that redefines the bowling experience by placing players in a vibrant cosmic arena. The game challenges your precision, skill, and timing as you aim to score points by knocking down pins in various celestial-themed lanes. Each game session offers a unique adventure, filled with stunning visuals and dynamic gameplay.", "short_description": "Strike Master: The Ultimate VR Bowling Experience\n\nWelcome to \"Strike Master,\" where the classic sport of bowling transcends the ordinary and enters a realm of immersive virtual reality. Get ready to embark on a cosmic adventure that transforms traditional bowling into an exhilarating and futuristic experience. Whether you're a seasoned bowler or new to the game, \"Strike Master\" offers a fresh and captivating way to enjoy this beloved sport."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/strike-master-vr/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "LC Invention", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/strike-master-vr", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1592192974313489"}, {"id": "1436351953220286"}, {